# Commit Message

When suggesting or writing git commit messages, **always use English only**.

- Use [Conventional Commits](https://www.conventionalcommits.org/) format when appropriate (e.g., `feat:`, `fix:`, `docs:`)
- Keep the subject line under 72 characters
- Provide body/details in English as well
